<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Gay Bards</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
This would have to be one of my funniest ideas. Think of it...a pair of bards, probably a Half-Elf and a Wood-Elf...who are bracingly homosexual, and don't care. We're talkin'...phallic innuendoes, dedications to each others' rears...the whole deal. This would have to be played by a two-box or by two very close friends, but the comic potential is endless.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Band</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
This is my second favorite, also including bards. This would need 3-5 bards who ALWAYS group together, each specializing in a certain instrument. There would have to be a lead singer, of course. What kind of music would they play? Why, the obvious of course.<br>
<br>
Death Metal.<br>
<br>
And, of course, after each performance, there would be groupies, flocks of Wood Elf fangirls who scream and squeal and whatnot. They could even break up and have a come-back tour accross Norrath! It'd be great.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Cursed Cat</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
This would be a Vah Shir Beastlord, no contest. The background for this would be that a normal, every-day feral jungle cat or otherwise somehow offended a god or lesser power. Perhaps by spraying one of their altars or somesuch. As punishment, they were given an anthropomorphic body, but nothing else. So they can't speak, but can understand, and communicate with gestures, grunts, etc. They would be very wild and feral, and act entirely on instinct. This would be the most difficult to play, by far.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Confused/Horny Paladin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Ah, yes...Most definately an E.Marr follower, this is a Paladin who loves everything SO much, that his behavior is often times questionable. Much like Roberto Binini, he is &quot;bursting with the love of a thousand buttocks&quot;, or, his &quot;pelvis is as joyous as Jupiter in a Vestial Virgin meeting&quot;, etc. He's flirtacious, he's wonton, he's a scallywag if there ever was one..<br>
<br>
